section.para:
In the 3-way mode the input,stylesheets and result settings of the XSLT Processor dockable are disabled. You may only add parameters and run the transformation. To use this mode of the XSLT Processor, you need a view split into three with :
a source XML document, in xml mode;
a stylesheet, in xsl mode;
a result buffer, in any mode.

listitem.para:
only the Xalan XSLT processor is bundled for the moment. It's the default
  choice and also the platform's default (maybe in an outdated version);
  it is compatible with XSLT version 1.0 (http://www.w3.org/TR/xslt);
